{"tid":2359727,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來得三十！夏世三生日想要……阿閪左腳！","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T06:52:52.000Z","uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4fec80f9447db5eeafc414e27d7c46b4979251","tid":2359727,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"Now Sports】皇家馬德里球星夏薩特周四度過30歲生日，他想得到美斯的左腳、基斯坦奴朗拿度的爭勝心、施丹的「卡士」作為禮物。太貪心吧？<br />\n皇家馬德里球星夏薩特（Eden Hazard）於1月7日過30歲生日，當他受訪問及想收到甚麼生日禮物時，竟然貪心得要齊3大球王級人馬的長處，「我會想得到美斯的左腳、基斯坦奴朗拿度的爭勝心，以及施丹的卡士。」 至於最想合作的名宿，夏沙特提到自己已經跟施丹和亨利在球會和國家隊合作過，因此，他最想合作是阿根廷的名宿列基美：「列基美是我唯一未遇過的偶像，小時候看過他所有比賽片段。若有一天遇到他，我一定會告訴他。」 <br />\n夏薩特坦言自己享受足球，一旦對足球失去快樂，我將毫不留戀地掛靴。自加盟皇馬後長期受傷兼缺態，他與皇馬完約時將是33歲零6個月，屆時有可能告別球壇。"},{"pid":"d35b9f4803838396dbea2a4a4f79439277864067","tid":2359727,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0104%2Fd2f6d0b8g00qmdyg102f2c0009q005gc.gif&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0104%252Fd2f6d0b8g00qmdyg102f2c0009q005gc.gif%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Dgif&h=4f4aafe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0104%2F944f0661g00qmdy4m01d2c0009q005ic.gif&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0104%252F944f0661g00qmdy4m01d2c0009q005ic.gif%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Dgif&h=92d4ddfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0104%2F1388569dg00qmdy7e03nxc0009q005fc.gif&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;qu